{"tid":2030071,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"Permutation題目","createTime":"2020-05-22T14:15:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T02:51:41.000Z","uid":119527,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dd237b4649905092bd491a245172c0bbee910c22","tid":2030071,"uid":119527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:15:53.000Z","msg":"有無人識依條permutation 題目<br />\n<br />\n1) Pauline has 1 dictionary, 1 comic and 5 different fictions. She wants to put 4 books on the lower shelf and 3 books on the upper shelf. If the dictionary and the comic are put in different shelf, find the number of arrangements of the books."},{"pid":"32bd260927c5cd93a1322fe1883387f81449c52b","tid":2030071,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:30:20.000Z","msg":"2 x 7P7 x 4 x 5"},{"pid":"9fbc25f68137ef93c94cc966b5adb75e56fc1f87","tid":2030071,"uid":119527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32bd260927c5cd93a1322fe1883387f81449c52b","tid":2030071,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:30:20.000Z","msg":"2 x 7P7 x 4 x 5"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T15:00:45.000Z","msg":"Answer 係2880"},{"pid":"d0af323f7b8d6c4e7c4c4b192ca8400b4bafbd78","tid":2030071,"uid":58599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T15:03:49.000Z","msg":"5!x4x3x2"},{"pid":"44d55a194271d65ab6d991cd41896e2d0c7c8e8b","tid":2030071,"uid":278118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T15:04:00.000Z","msg":"2(4)(3)5!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2= A上B下；B上A下<br />\n<br />\n4 = 4位選1位<br />\n<br />\n3 = 3位選1位<br />\n<br />\n5！ 淨低5 本排喺5 個位"},{"pid":"1218b3042ec26d3aeba9bc461a90f2c006d284cb","tid":2030071,"uid":210998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T15:05:36.000Z","msg":"7! - 5C2*3!*4! -5C1*3!*4!"},{"pid":"9f0f2e00e01bdb26f0f79e438e10f434ff0f64b8","tid":2030071,"uid":58599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0af323f